Text: Life goes on and i keep asking questions on my head. Everytime someone tells
  me about their trip to a different country i cant help my self. I just sit next
  to that persona and imagine in my head what a big world is... Culture give us such
  and amazing view of what we believe in, and what we are made of learn and take the
  best from that place. Create conexions around the world is what us Humans were suppose
  to do i want to be the voice and the eyes to a new culture. Theres so much to learn
  and writte about ...
